  <brief_title>Regular Physical Exercise and Salt Diet on Coronary Artery Disease in Patients With Prehypertension(RESTRAIN Pre-HT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Regular Physical Exercise and Salt Diet Effect on Progression of Coronary Disease in Patients With Prehypertension</official_title>
